headline.main: Government Forces Recapture Northern Afghanistan District
headline.print_headline: Government Forces Recapture Northern Afghanistan District

lead_paragraph: Syrian peace talks are expected to conclude later on Friday with an "agreed agenda" and a plan to resume negotiations later this month in Geneva, Western diplomats said.
